name: Caphector'sWeatherStation
0:
”Alexa, ask weather station about the weather”
”Alexa, ask weather station about the temperature”
”Alexa, ask weather station about the humidity”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: weather station
des: This skill can report weather data from Caphector's personal weather station in Fremont, CA. It supports temperature, humidity, rain, pressure, wind and dew point, as well as a general weather request.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
